description:
The Protagonist in this story and the only character who isn`t a futanari.
Searching for a new form of stimulation she`s invited to join the futa club as a "service member" by http://anidb.net/ch62584 [Sumika Oohashi].
Despite being delegated to the status of the futa club`s cock sleeve, she`s more than satisfied with that.
name: Niimura Akane
